quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Aif, Lam, Ra. These are the signs of the Manifest Book"
  12,2,Indeed We have sent it down as an Arabic Quran so that you may exercise your reason
  12,3,"We will recount to you the best of narratives in what We have revealed to you of this Quran, and indeed prior to it you were among those who are unaware [of it]"
  12,4,"When Joseph said to his father, ‘Father! I saw eleven planets, and the sun and the moon: I saw them prostrating themselves before me,’"
  12,5,"he said, ‘My son, do not recount your dream to your brothers, lest they should devise schemes against you. Satan is indeed man’s manifest enemy"
  12,6,"That is how your Lord will choose you, and teach you the interpretation of dreams, and complete His blessing upon you and upon the house of Jacob, just as He completed it earlier for your fathers, Abraham and Isaac. Your Lord is indeed all-knowing and all-wise.’"